    silent_salt: "color-header{silent_salt:Silence Eternal} <br>Eclipse: status{dmg_dealt_up|und_buff} DMG +22.5% for 15 sec; stacks up to x1<br>Rooted: 2.5 sec<br>Silence Eternal: status{silence} Silence for 2 sec every 1 sec over 3 sec<br>color-header{silent_salt:Lunar Slash} <br>Moon Slash DMG: steel{%{attr1}} of ATK + 25.5% of Max HP (Cookies), darkness{427.3%} of ATK (Others)<br>Moon Slash DMG Resist Bypass: 40.0%<br>Moon Slash: Petrified 2 sec + status{weakness} Taken DMG +40.0% for 15 sec; stacks up to x1<br>Moon Explosion DMG: x6 hits dealing steel{%{attr2}} of ATK + 25.0% of Max HP (Cookies), darkness{183.2%} of ATK (Others) per hit<br>Moon Explosion DMG Resist Bypass: 40.0%<br>status{dmg_dealt_down} DMG Dealt by Enemies: -25.0% for 10 sec after Moon Explosion; stacks up to x1<br>status{consuming_darkness} Consuming Darkness (Darkness-type DMG Targets): CRIT% -5.0%, Healing -5.0% for 8 sec; stacks up to x3<br>status{forsaken_freedom|und_buff} color-header{silent_salt:Forsaken Freedom} <br>Immune to Cooldown-impairing effects<br>When inflicted with Cooldown-impairing effects: status{hp_shield} HP Shield of 20.0% Max HP + status{dmg_down} DMG Resist +15.0% + status{cooldown_recovery_up} Cooldown Recovery +25.0% for 5 sec; stacks up to x1<br>Debuff Resist +35.0%<br>Max HP +35.0%<br>DMG Resist +35.0%<br>color-header{silent_salt:Beast Passive: Fury of the Catacombs} <br>status{fury_of_the_catacombs|und_debuff} Fury of the Catacombs: Cooldown Recovery -25.0%, Dealt DMG -25.0%<br>Searing Seal: x1 per 1 sec + x3 when target uses skill + x4 when casting Moon Explosion<br>At x7 Searing Seal Stacks: Punishment & Searing Seal reset<br>Punishment DMG: x3 hits dealing steel{189.9%} of ATK per hit + 35.0% of Max HP (Cookies) + darkness{273.5%} of ATK (Others)<br>Punishment DMG Resist Bypass: 35.0%<br>Punishment status{silence|und_debuff} Silence: 1.5 sec<br>color-header{silent_salt:Beast Passive: Wrath of the Catacombs} <br>Activated when Allies' Total HP drops to 70.0%<br>Skill Cooldown reset + status{invulnerable|und_buff} Invulnerability for 1 sec and Silent Demise<br>If Silent Demise or Moon Explosion are activated or 15 sec passes, Wrath of the Catacombs ends, triggering Punishment<br>Punishment DMG: x3 hits dealing steel{480.5%} of ATK + 45.0% of Max HP (Cookies), darkness{325.0%} of ATK (Others), per hit<br>Punishment DMG Resist Bypass: 40.0%<br>Punishment status{silence|und_debuff} Silence: 1.5 sec<br>If a Cookie's HP drops below 3.5% from Punishment, they are immediately defeated",
